      value: 18
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 3700041176858542214, guid: b794de413864f89419c61eade627ddc0,
        type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_text
      value: '''raik, you were always alive, you are a part of this universe, I was
        not the one to bring you to life, I didn''t choose you, you choose me, I
        was drawn to that rock in the middle of the forest, you may not know it,
        but we moiran have learnt a lot from you, it is unfortunate that we must
        part, But we moiran must end, I cannot tell you how your journey ends raik.
        But u don''t have to do this alone. Maybe ask the tairan for help. Though
        knowing them, they won''t make it easy. Remember raik, you have been given
        the most precious resource of all, Time. Share it wisely.


        Good
        bye dear friend'''
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
